'''Ultrasonix Medical Corporation''' is a [[sonography]] equipment company specializing in high quality medical [[ultrasound]] equipment. Founded in 2000, the company developed the first Open Research Ultrasound Platform called OpenSonix. In 2009, Ultrasonix introduced the SonixTouch Ultrasound System, a leading system configurable for emerging Ultrasound Applications.

